Package: SingleCellHT
Title: Single-Cell Hierarchical Tensor (SCHT) Creation Pipeline in R
Version: 1.2.0
Date: 2025-02-17
Authors@R: c(
    person("Siyuan", "Wu", email = "thaddeus.wu@jcu.edu.au", role = c("aut", "cre")),
    person("Ulf", "Schmitz", role = "aut"))
Description: This script takes raw gene- and transcript-level count matrices,
    performs a series of quality control and normalisation steps, and finally
    creates a Single-Cell Hierarchical Tensor (SCHT).
